import React from 'react';
import { Container, Header, Grid, Image, List, Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import PropTypes from 'prop-types';
import vk from '../../../Images/vk.png';

const HomepageHeading = ({ bool }) => {
  console.log("this is what =" + bool)
  return (
    <Container text>
      {/* <Header
        as='h2'
        content='Imagine-a-Company'
        inverted
      style={{
        fontSize: bool ? '1.5em' : '2em',
        fontWeight: 'normal',
        marginBottom: 0,
        marginTop: bool ? '1em' : '1em',
      }}
      /> */}

      <Segment inverted vertical style={{ padding: '0em', margin:'0em'}}>
        <Container>
          <Grid inverted stackable>
            <Grid.Row>
              <Grid.Column>
                <Header inverted as='h4'/>
                <List link inverted>
                  <List.Item as='a'>Sitemap</List.Item>
                  <List.Item as='a'>Contact Us</List.Item>
                  <List.Item as='a'>Religious Ceremonies</List.Item>
                  <List.Item as='a'>Gazebo Plans</List.Item>
                </List>
              </Grid.Column>
            </Grid.Row>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Segment>

      <Grid columns="2" inverted stackable>
        <Grid.Row textAlign='center' className="RowPadding">
          <Grid.Column width={4}>
            aa
          </Grid.Column>
          <Grid.Column width={12} className="headerImageBoxShadow">
            <Image className="headerImage"
              src={vk}
            />
          </Grid.Column>
        </Grid.Row>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  )
}

HomepageHeading.propTypes = {
  mobile: PropTypes.bool
}

export default HomepageHeading;
